<lyrics>[V1]
 1-(kẖlqtk ky tḥyạ bḥby wtbqy̱ ly ạ̹bnạ ynʿm bḥnạny
 qlby mntẓr lk yạ ạ̹bny wạlsmạʾ hy bytk ạltẖạny)2
 hl ận ạlạ̉wạn lthdyny qlbk ạ̉rjʿh nqyạaⁿ fy tẖwạny
 wạ̉ḥyy fyh lmsẗ mn rwḥy wạ̉skn fyh bmlỷ wjdạny
 ạlqrạr- yạ ạ̹bny ṭmỷn qlby mty̱ tfyq mn gẖybwbẗ ạlḥyạẗ fạ̉ḥyyk
 mty̱ trjʿ lnhry lyrwyk wthll ạlmlạỷkh tḥyyk
 wtsẖdw ạlsmạʾ thnyk wyʿzf ạlkwn lḥnạaⁿ ysẖjyk
 2-(tʿạly̱ yạạ̹bny ạ̉ḍmk lṣdry fysmʿ qlbk ạ̉nsẖwdẗ kẖfqạty
 wrnm ly bqytẖạrh fmk trnymẗ ạlʿwdh ftfrḥ smwạty)2
 klmạthạ mnqwsẖh bdmy qd tḥy fyk dẖkry̱ ạ̉sẖjạny
 ʿlhạ tʿydk lḥḍn qlby ạlmsẖtạq lmn mnḥth ḥyạty</lyrics>
<title>ạlrb ynạdy</title>
</song>